---

<Layout title="Travel & Culture – Cristóbal Maturana" description="Travel and culture documentary photography by Cristóbal Maturana.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Travel & Culture</h1>
      <p>Observing the world, honestly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="gallery-intro">
        <p>A visual exploration of places, people, and everyday life across different cultures. Through a documentary approach and natural light, I capture authentic moments as they unfold — focusing on atmosphere, human connection, and the subtle details that define each destination. Honest images shaped by perspective and experience.</p>
      </div>
      <Gallery images={images} layout="masonry" columns={3} />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gallery-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
